<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>VMO-Link</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />
 
    <!-- Google / Search Engine Tags -->
    <meta itemprop="name" content="VMOLink">
    <meta itemprop="description" content="A professional looking link will increase brand recognition and consumer trust in your communications—which in turn inspires even more engagement with your links.">
    <meta itemprop="image" content="https://vmojp.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/banner/vmo-link-2.png">
    
    <!-- Facebook Meta Tags -->
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://vmo.link">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="VMOLink">
    <meta property="og:description" content="A professional looking link will increase brand recognition and consumer trust in your communications—which in turn inspires even more engagement with your links.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://vmojp.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/banner/vmo-link-2.png">
    
    <!-- Twitter Meta Tags -->
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="VMOLink">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="A professional looking link will increase brand recognition and consumer trust in your communications—which in turn inspires even more engagement with your links.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://vmojp.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/banner/vmo-link.png">

    <link href="/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro:ital,wght@0,200;0,400;0,700;1,200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://pro.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.10.0/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-AYmEC3Yw5cVb3ZcuHtOA93w35dYTsvhLPVnYs9eStHfGJvOvKxVfELGroGkvsg+p" crossorigin="anonymous"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">
    <!-- Global site tag (gtag.js) - Google Analytics -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-PNS8GEJH5M"></script>
    <script>
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
        gtag('js', new Date());

        gtag('config', 'G-PNS8GEJH5M');
  </script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container-design">
    <div class="main">
        <div class="header-design">
            <div class="header__logo">
                <a href="/">
                    <img src="/img/vmo-link-2.png" alt="Logo">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="header__actions">
                <% if (!logged){%>
                    <a class="btn_authen" href="/auth/google">
                        Login with&nbsp;&nbsp;
                        <em class="fab fa-google font-size-25"></em>
                    </a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a class="btn_authen" href="/auth/manager">Manager</a>
                    <a class="btn_authen" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-design">
            <div aria-live="polite" aria-atomic="true" class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                <div class="toast" role="alert" style="position: fixed;" aria-live="assertive" aria-atomic="true" data-delay="6000">
                  <div class="toast-header toast-design">
                    <strong class="mr-auto text-warning">SHORTEN ERROR</strong>
                    <button type="button" class="ml-2 mb-1 close" data-dismiss="toast" aria-label="Close">
                      <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                    </button>
                  </div>
                  <div id="display-error" class="toast-body text-muted toast-design" style="font-size: 1.5rem; min-height: 100px; min-width: 300px; text-align: center;">
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content__title">
                <h1 class="mt-3">Welcome to VMOLink</h1>
                <h3 class="mt-2" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Build a shortenLink page for your business and everyone</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="content__body">
<!--                Shorten link display-->
                <div class="flex-between" style="align-items: center;">
                    <div class="flex-center width-100">
                        <div class="shorten_link">
                            <p id="shorten-link" style="color:#2200CC"></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-center align-item-center margin-left-20">
                        <button id="btn-copy" class="btn--orange mb-2" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="click to copy">Copy</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
<!--                Original link input-->
                <div class="flex-between">
                    <div class="flex-center width-100">
                        <input id="long-link" class="link-input" type="text" placeholder="Enter that long link...">
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-center align-item-center margin-left-20">
                        <% if (logged){%>
                            <button id="get-short-link-user" class="btn--orange">Shorten</button>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <button id="get-short-link-guest" class="btn--orange">Shorten</button>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>
<!--                Option display-->
                <div class="padding-left-right-20 margin-top-20">
                    <div class="flex-between">
                        <label class="checkbox__container">
                            <input id="option-advanced" type="checkbox">
                                Advanced options
                            <span class="checkmark"></span>
                        </label>
                        <p class="note margin-top-7" style="margin-left: 1%">*You need to login to set password, expire date and customer the link address</p>
                    </div>
                    <div id="option-div">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="introduce">
        <div class="introduce__arrow">
            <img src="/img/arrow.png" alt="arrow">
        </div>
        <h2 class="introduce__title">VMOLink will strongly support your branding</h2>
        <div class="introduce__content">
            <div class="card-design">
                <p class="card__title">Inspire trust</p>
                <div class="card__image handshake_background">
                    <img src="/img/introduce1.png" alt="Handshake">
                </div>
                <div class="card__content" style="text-align: justify;">
                    A professional looking link will increase brand recognition and consumer trust in your
                    communications—which in turn inspires even more engagement with your links.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-design" style="text-align: justify;">
                <p class="card__title">Managing links</p>
                <div class="card__image asset_background">
                    <img src="/img/introduce2.png" alt="Asset">
                </div>
                <div class="card__content">
                    With advanced options, you can create, protect and delete your links.
                    You can also monitor them with detailed statistics which will help you to easily manage your link list.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-design" style="text-align: justify;">
                <p class="card__title">Boost results</p>
                <div class="card__image boost_background">
                    <img src="/img/introduce3.png" alt="Boost">
                </div>
                <div class="card__content">
                    On top of better deliverability and click-through, rich link-level data gives you crucial insight
                    into your link engagement so your team can make smarter decisions around its content and communications.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© Made by VMOGROUP</p>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="/vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/home.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
